## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- We will manually submit the `/register` form, observe the UI update, and verify a user row is created in the Supabase `auth.users` table.
- We will click the confirmation link in the email (if enabled) to test the callback route `/api/auth/callback`.
- We will try logging in via `/login` with incorrect credentials to verify the error state displays correctly.
- We will try logging in with correct credentials to verify the user is instantly redirected to the Home page and the session is stored in cookies.
